This project requires a MySQL DB configured on the local machine. Please take a look at the script directory where i create the database. 

We can use spring properties to set up the initial database. Please fix these settings before you evolve this project (since the DDL will be run everytime Spring initializes). Take a look at src/main/resources/application.properties file. 

spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create
spring.jpa.show-sql=true

Read this project in tandem with jpah2 which is the same code but uses h2 database (easier to experiment)
